text.tspan: Define your password (login jean.dupont for jean.dupont@ens-lyon.fr by default but may differ)
Build your schedule : you will be able to edit slots only if the slotstatus is to your own status
You can book three rooms maximum at the same time: your office, your workplace and a single extra room (analysis, meeting)
For your office and workplace, there are shortcuts that you can click on, and an extra option to add both simultaneously
For the extra room, you have to click on the room on the maps, you will see the name of the room updated
You can check the occupation of the room thanks to the graph for the selected day
(green line : occupation after your slot, violet line : before) and the table below.
